1
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:17,600
Once he gets married,

2
00:00:18,100 --> 00:00:19,800
one week after, he can take the position.

3
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:21,600
I've looked for the auspicious time.

4
00:00:22,100 --> 00:00:23,000
A month and a half?

5
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,600
The auspicious time for wedding can't be postponed.

6
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:26,600
No matter what, I'll interrupt your wedding.

7
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:29,600
but you won't be able to inherit from Father.

8
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,100
My brother's happiness must come first.

9
00:00:31,100 --> 00:00:32,800
Tian is getting married in a month and a half?

10
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:33,600
Yes.

11
00:00:34,100 --> 00:00:35,600
I would like you to send me news.

12
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:37,100
I will handle this myself.

13
00:00:37,100 --> 00:00:38,600
If you are successful,

14
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,900
I will give you the medicine formula used to treat your sister.

15
00:00:41,900 --> 00:00:43,600
Just tell me who do you want me to kill.

16
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:46,600
I want you to kill the Song's eldest son.

17
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:49,600
And if this is revealed,

18
00:00:50,100 --> 00:00:53,600
Tian's secret that we're struggling to hide may be exposed again.

19
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:54,600
What is Tian's secret?

20
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:57,100
We have asked herbal shops and pharmacies across the town,

21
00:00:57,100 --> 00:00:59,600
but no one can explain about this mushroom.

22
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:01,600
Then our assumption might be true

23
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:03,000
that this mushroom is probably related to the chaos in our house.

24
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:03,600
Right.

25
00:01:04,100 --> 00:01:06,600
In the past, Song family had a Chinese doctor

26
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:07,600
Where is he now?

27
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:09,600
Doctor Qi who was here?

28
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:11,600
I heard that he's back to Chonburi.

29
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:14,600
If we meet Doctor Qi, we'll know what mushroom it is,

30
00:01:15,100 --> 00:01:17,600
and if it has anything to do with the mystery in our home.

31
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:02,600
I call everyone to come here today

32
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,600
because I have good news to inform you.

33
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,600
In another month and a half,

34
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,600
there will be an auspicious event of Tian.

35
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:19,600
So I want to take everyone to pay respects to the god

36
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:23,600
at the Song family's shrine in Chonburi.

37
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:30,600
So I want everyone to get ready.

38
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,600
We will depart tomorrow.

39
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,600
This is a good opportunity.

40
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:50,600
If we go to Chonburi, we'll get to find Doctor Qi.

41
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:55,600
Soon we'll know how this mushroom is related to our family.

42
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,600
Yes.

43
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:08,600
Yang, what if the thing we suspect comes true?

44
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:14,600
That Tian's secret made Madam Li kill a man like Chan said.

45
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:18,600
Why do you believe that Tian has a secret?

46
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:22,600
I've secretly overheard Madam Li talking to Jia.

47
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,600
I wanted to ask you a few days ago.

48
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:29,600
Yang, you knew it, right?

49
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,600
What is Tian's secret?

50
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,600
Yang.

51
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:39,600
If you know it, please tell me.

52
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:43,100
If there's a problem, we can solve it together.

53
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:45,600
I'm worried about Tian as well.

54
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,600
But we can't fix anything.

55
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:54,600
Can't fix ? Why not?

56
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:58,600
Since Tian is a good man.

57
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:01,600
What secret that is so serious and sinful?

58
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,600
It should be nothing.

59
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:08,600
Is there any secret that is too hard to fix it?

60
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:13,600
But it's hard to say, I can't say it.

61
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,600
Even though you can't say it, you must speak.

62
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,600
Father.

63
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,600
What is Tian's secret?

64
00:05:45,224 --> 00:05:46,512
Bao.

65
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,600
What's the matter, Madam?

66
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,904
Where is Mr. Song?

67
00:05:51,408 --> 00:05:53,600
When I came here, he wasn't here anymore.

68
00:05:58,424 --> 00:06:02,368
He isn't in the bedroom. Where has he gone?

69
00:06:04,872 --> 00:06:06,176
So what is it?

70
00:06:06,744 --> 00:06:09,072
You guys are talking about Tian's secret.

71
00:06:09,872 --> 00:06:11,816
What is his secret?

72
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:19,720
There are many chaos in our family right now.

73
00:06:19,736 --> 00:06:22,600
Since Dong died, strange things happen.

74
00:06:23,992 --> 00:06:26,192
Li acts as if she has something hidden.

75
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:30,600
Chan blames her for killing Dong.

76
00:06:31,536 --> 00:06:35,320
And now you two are also hiding something from me as well?

77
00:06:38,984 --> 00:06:40,128
Bua.

78
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:44,136
Why did you ask Yang about Tian's secret?

79
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:47,408
Well...

80
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:51,600
I'm just worried about Mr. Tian.

81
00:06:51,608 --> 00:06:58,600
I think he might be stressed about the secret Madam Chan usually mentions, Sir.

82
00:06:59,688 --> 00:07:00,792
Really?

83
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:02,008
Yes.

84
00:07:04,408 --> 00:07:05,600
Yang.

85
00:07:07,272 --> 00:07:09,456
You said it can't be undone.

86
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,060
What do you mean?

87
00:07:12,064 --> 00:07:14,024
Well, if you heard it just now,

88
00:07:14,048 --> 00:07:18,408
you should hear the same that I can't said it. It's difficult to explain.

89
00:07:18,416 --> 00:07:20,920
Are you going to play this trick?

90
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:22,888
Fine.

91
00:07:25,112 --> 00:07:28,304
Getting on my nerves to hide the truth?

92
00:07:30,096 --> 00:07:32,856
I will ask Tian and Li instead.

93
00:07:36,216 --> 00:07:37,600
Okay.

94
00:07:42,976 --> 00:07:44,656
But if you know it,

95
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,840
don't scold Tian.

96
00:07:52,312 --> 00:07:56,030
I asked him to keep me company last night to go out and disobeyed your order.

97
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:58,600
Then Bua doubted this and caught me.

98
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:00,600
So she just asked me that's all.

99
00:08:03,408 --> 00:08:04,776
This is it?

100
00:08:06,272 --> 00:08:08,024
That you said you can't fix it.

101
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:10,208
Don't think that it's just this small.

102
00:08:10,496 --> 00:08:12,832
Last time I got beaten until my back hurt.

103
00:08:13,008 --> 00:08:15,808
Tian is a good man, so he kept thinking

104
00:08:15,832 --> 00:08:18,600
and was afraid that if I get caught, I'll get hit again.

105
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:22,608
It's not very serious.

106
00:08:22,616 --> 00:08:25,400
Don't punish Mr. Yang, Sir.

107
00:08:32,768 --> 00:08:33,848
Yang.

108
00:08:36,464 --> 00:08:37,728
I'm your father.

109
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:42,600
You're lying.

110
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,128
Do you think that I don't know this?

111
00:09:05,912 --> 00:09:07,016
Secret?

112
00:09:07,648 --> 00:09:10,464
Does Mr. Tian really have something hidden?

113
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:14,600
Your conversation hasn't finished yet?

114
00:09:15,256 --> 00:09:17,856
At first I thought there was only Chan.

115
00:09:18,248 --> 00:09:20,552
Now Bua and Mr. Yang also talked about it.

116
00:09:20,568 --> 00:09:21,664
That's right.

117
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,600
If Chan talked about it alone,

118
00:09:26,048 --> 00:09:29,600
I would think that she was trying to slander Li.

119
00:09:30,432 --> 00:09:32,600
Or does Mr. Yang want to help Madam Chan?

120
00:09:32,936 --> 00:09:36,624
They're mother and son. They might want to help each other.

121
00:09:38,208 --> 00:09:39,464
No.

122
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:43,032
Even if this son is useless,

123
00:09:43,512 --> 00:09:45,312
he's not that kind of guy.

124
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,392
What are you going to do?

125
00:09:47,688 --> 00:09:50,224
Forcing Mr. Yang to speak the truth?

126
00:09:51,496 --> 00:09:55,704
Even if you I force him, he'll probably lie like this time.

127
00:09:57,136 --> 00:09:58,656
Tian's secret

128
00:09:59,256 --> 00:10:01,896
is not just about escaping to hang out like he said.

129
00:10:03,168 --> 00:10:06,440
But now we can't do anything besides being silent.

130
00:10:06,792 --> 00:10:09,864
We have to keep an eye on all my children and wives.

131
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,824
Especially Li.

132
00:10:12,792 --> 00:10:14,744
What do you suspect Madam Li?

133
00:10:15,112 --> 00:10:18,016
Now do you think what she said

134
00:10:18,016 --> 00:10:22,208
that Madam killed Dong to hide Mr. Tian's secret was true?

135
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:25,080
I won't believe anything

136
00:10:25,856 --> 00:10:27,600
until I have evidence.

137
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,600
This job is very important.

138
00:10:47,624 --> 00:10:49,504
Don't make a mistake.

139
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:51,472
If you are successful,

140
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:55,448
I will give you the medicine formula used to treat your sister.

141
00:10:55,456 --> 00:10:59,944
You will be free. You can do whatever you want in the future.

142
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:04,928
You don't have to take my job in exchange for medicine to cure your sister again.

143
00:11:11,696 --> 00:11:15,600
Mr. Ma said that you can't make a mistake this time.

144
00:11:15,608 --> 00:11:20,152
When you get there, notice the person carrying a blue handkerchief.

145
00:11:20,168 --> 00:11:26,056
She will be the one to lure Mr. Song's eldest son out for you to kill him.

146
00:11:32,424 --> 00:11:35,944
Prepare enough food for everyone.

147
00:11:35,944 --> 00:11:38,808
We are staying overnight. Don't miss it.

148
00:11:38,816 --> 00:11:41,768
So once we reach the shrine, you won't have to buy it again.

149
00:11:41,776 --> 00:11:42,776
Yes, Madam.

150
00:11:43,368 --> 00:11:47,176
And is the stuff I let you prepared ready?

151
00:11:47,184 --> 00:11:48,580
You're welcome.

152
00:11:48,584 --> 00:11:51,136
- So carry the stuff to the car.
- Yes, Madam.

153
00:11:53,912 --> 00:11:55,744
What is the stuff?

154
00:11:57,896 --> 00:12:00,600
Just in case I meet Dr. Qi, Madam.

155
00:12:00,608 --> 00:12:04,016
I've heard that he had returned from China and has lived in Chonburi.

156
00:12:04,016 --> 00:12:08,720
Song Family visit there every year. He might hear the news and visit us.

157
00:12:09,872 --> 00:12:12,600
I haven't seen him in a long time.

158
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:17,496
If we meet this time, you will be very happy.

159
00:12:18,928 --> 00:12:19,872
Yes, Madam.

160
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:25,830
I have knowledge of herbs to take care of you and Mr. Song like today

161
00:12:25,848 --> 00:12:28,400
because he taught me.

162
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:31,170
He has always been considerate of me

163
00:12:31,184 --> 00:12:34,416
like a teacher and a brother to me.

164
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,600
Let's go.

165
00:12:43,168 --> 00:12:46,128
Bua, let's go.

166
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:50,600
Everything is ready. Let's go.

167
00:12:54,224 --> 00:12:57,696
When you get there, keep an eye on Tian.

168
00:12:57,704 --> 00:12:59,824
Don't let him out of sight.

169
00:12:59,832 --> 00:13:01,760
Keep reporting me.

170
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,600
Yes, Madam.

171
00:13:06,416 --> 00:13:08,984
If you're ready, let's go.

172
00:13:38,264 --> 00:13:40,600
Bua, the car is over there.

173
00:13:40,616 --> 00:13:43,550
Yes, Mr. Tian. Let's go, Mr. Yang.

174
00:13:43,568 --> 00:13:44,600
Yes.

175
00:13:51,504 --> 00:13:54,600
You guys, get in the car now.

176
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:00,000
Chonburi

177
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:25,600
Mr. Song, please come in.

178
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:42,600
You must be tired from traveling. I'll find something for you to drink.

179
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,600
Thanks.

180
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:50,600
You brought a lot of people this year.

181
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:53,600
Our family is having a big event.

182
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,600
It's Tian's wedding.

183
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:59,600
So I brought everyone to pay respects to the Buddha

184
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:01,600
to bless for smooth wedding.

185
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:05,600
Congratulations to Mr. Tian for your wedding.

186
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:10,600
Are you going to have grandchild for Mr. Song after marriage?

187
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:12,600
It must be like that.

188
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,600
What are you waiting for?

189
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:15,600
Right?

190
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,600
Tian.

191
00:15:57,600 --> 00:16:00,600
Your face wasn't quite good then.

192
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:02,600
Are you sick?

193
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,600
I'm just tired. It's been a long journey.

194
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:09,600
I thought there was something uncomfortable for you.

195
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,600
Time flies, Tian.

196
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:24,600
I still remembers this feeling very well.

197
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:27,600
I still remember the picture when you were a child.

198
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:30,600
You two brothers running and playing around.

199
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:33,600
You are getting married soon.

200
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:38,600
You're growing up to be an adult to take care of Song Family

201
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:43,600
and continue the work after me.

202
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,600
Father.

203
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:50,600
Actually, I still enjoy my work.

204
00:16:51,100 --> 00:16:52,600
No need to get married now.

205
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:55,600
Are you having a hard time?

206
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:01,600
In the past, I've never discussed directly with you.

207
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:04,600
I've always talked through your mom.

208
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:07,600
If you have any trouble,

209
00:17:08,600 --> 00:17:09,600
you can tell me.

210
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:13,600
I'm your father anyway.

211
00:17:18,600 --> 00:17:20,600
I'm ready to do everything

212
00:17:21,600 --> 00:17:23,600
to make you happy, Tian.

213
00:17:28,600 --> 00:17:30,600
You're not in love with Pin, right?

214
00:17:32,600 --> 00:17:34,600
Is she not good?

215
00:17:36,600 --> 00:17:40,600
Or do you already have a lover?

216
00:17:41,100 --> 00:17:41,600
No, I don't.

217
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:47,600
Tian.

218
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:50,600
Since you were child,

219
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:53,600
you were a good,

220
00:17:54,600 --> 00:17:55,600
hard-working boy.

221
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:59,600
When you grow up, you have done a good job.

222
00:17:59,600 --> 00:18:01,600
The employees all love you.

223
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:04,600
I saw you growing up every day.

224
00:18:09,600 --> 00:18:11,600
But it seems like it's me

225
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:17,600
who is far from you day by day.

226
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:22,600
I still remember well when you were a child,

227
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:25,600
when you saw something,

228
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:29,600
you would always tell me about it.

229
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:32,600
But now it's changed.

230
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:36,600
You never told me anything again.

231
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:45,600
Maybe it's because I am busy working.

232
00:18:47,600 --> 00:18:48,600
Is it too late?

233
00:18:50,600 --> 00:18:51,600
If today...

234
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:55,600
If I want to know about you.

235
00:18:57,600 --> 00:18:59,600
What do you want to know?

236
00:19:00,600 --> 00:19:01,600
Everything.

237
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:08,600
Or a secret that everyone is talking about.

238
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:14,600
You can tell me that too.

239
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,600
Father.

240
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:30,600
Tian.

241
00:19:31,100 --> 00:19:32,600
What are you guys talking?

242
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:42,600
It's nothing.

243
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:47,600
We were talking father and son stuff.

244
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:07,600
If we wait here and don't meet Doctor Qi,

245
00:20:08,600 --> 00:20:09,600
what should we do?

246
00:20:10,100 --> 00:20:11,600
Should we search for him?

247
00:20:12,100 --> 00:20:15,600
I think if we rush out to look for him, we could miss him.

248
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:19,600
We also don't know which part of Chonburi Doctor Qi lives in.

249
00:20:22,600 --> 00:20:23,600
Someone is here.

250
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:25,600
Excuse me, can I ask you something?

251
00:20:26,600 --> 00:20:28,600
Do you know someone named Doctor Qi?

252
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:32,100
He is a doctor who is good at Chinese herbal medicine.

253
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:33,600
He lives in Chonburi.

254
00:20:34,100 --> 00:20:36,600
Oh, there are many herbal medicine doctor here.

255
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:39,600
I can't remember all the names.

256
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:44,600
I'll ask others and tell you later if someone know him.

257
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:46,600
Thank you so much.

258
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:14,600
As a leader of Song Family,

259
00:21:15,600 --> 00:21:19,600
I'd like to be a representative to pay respect to the Buddha.

260
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:22,600
A representative

261
00:21:23,600 --> 00:21:26,600
to pay homage to all the gods that are here,

262
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:30,600
including all the ancestors of the Song Family.

263
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:32,600
Please help protect

264
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:35,600
everyone in our family,

265
00:21:36,600 --> 00:21:38,600
workers and servants.

266
00:21:39,600 --> 00:21:43,600
I wish everyone happiness and prosperity.

267
00:21:45,600 --> 00:21:49,600
May the business continue to prosper.

268
00:21:58,600 --> 00:22:00,600
Who is Mr. Song's eldest son?

269
00:22:09,600 --> 00:22:12,600
Mr. Yang and Mr. Tian sleep in the same room.

270
00:22:12,600 --> 00:22:17,600
And how are we going to lure him out and let Mr. Ma's man attack him?

271
00:22:18,600 --> 00:22:20,600
Has Mr. Ma's guy arrived yet?

272
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:23,600
(Whistling sound)

273
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:35,600
He's here.

274
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:39,600
Mr. Ma said that if the person is here,

275
00:22:40,100 --> 00:22:43,600
he'll send a signal as a bird chirping to let us know.

276
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:46,600
Find time to deliver the news.

277
00:22:47,600 --> 00:22:50,600
Tonight, I'm going to lure Tian to the garden

278
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:54,600
and let that person kill him.

279
00:22:55,600 --> 00:22:56,600
Yes, Madam.

280
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:13,600
Don't turn around, just tell me the plan.

281
00:23:14,300 --> 00:23:17,600
Tonight, go to Guanyin and then kill the man who are there.

282
00:23:33,600 --> 00:23:34,600
Mr. Yang,

283
00:23:36,600 --> 00:23:38,600
we have a big trouble.

284
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:49,600
Mr. Yang, Madam Chan said she wanted to go to the monkhood.

285
00:23:50,100 --> 00:23:51,600
What? Monkhood?

286
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:52,600
Yes.

287
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:58,600
Mother.

288
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:05,600
Are you going to be ordained?

289
00:24:06,600 --> 00:24:08,600
I went to talk to the monk teacher.

290
00:24:09,600 --> 00:24:13,600
Telling him that I wanted you to be become as the clan leader.

291
00:24:14,600 --> 00:24:15,600
But I can't

292
00:24:16,600 --> 00:24:17,600
because...

293
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:20,600
the position belongs to Tian.

294
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:23,600
So the teacher told me that I should know how to let go.

295
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:26,600
Otherwise, my heart will suffer.

296
00:24:29,600 --> 00:24:32,600
Now I realize that I was wrong.

297
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:35,600
So I want to get ordained

298
00:24:36,600 --> 00:24:39,600
in order to pay for my past mistakes.

299
00:24:41,600 --> 00:24:44,600
Someone like you are going to get ordained?

300
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:47,600
Yang, can you call Tian for me?

301
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:52,600
I have a lot of things that I want to talk to him.

302
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:54,600
I want to apologize.

303
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:56,600
I want to ask for forgiveness,

304
00:24:58,600 --> 00:25:01,600
so that I can follow the path of Dharma with peace of mind.

305
00:25:26,408 --> 00:25:27,600
Aunt Chan.

306
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,552
Tian.

307
00:25:31,552 --> 00:25:34,440
Yang said that you have something to talk to me.

308
00:25:34,968 --> 00:25:37,768
I don't know how I can say this feeling.

309
00:25:38,384 --> 00:25:42,384
In the past, what I did to you was wrong.

310
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:45,352
I always nitpick.

311
00:25:47,040 --> 00:25:49,552
Slandering Tian and Madam Li.

312
00:25:49,550 --> 00:25:51,600
Please don't be mad at me.

313
00:26:01,600 --> 00:26:03,600
She said that she would be ordained.

314
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,600
Really?

315
00:26:07,456 --> 00:26:08,600
Right.

316
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:12,128
I feel guilty.

317
00:26:13,888 --> 00:26:18,592
When I think of something serious I did to you,

318
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:22,008
I am even more shocked.

319
00:26:23,224 --> 00:26:24,208
Tian.

320
00:26:25,864 --> 00:26:29,600
In the past, when I did something,

321
00:26:29,700 --> 00:26:34,304
I did as I want regardless of the rights or wrongs.

322
00:26:34,904 --> 00:26:37,944
The more I think about it, the more I regret it.

323
00:26:37,952 --> 00:26:40,912
Tian, I'm very angry at myself.

324
00:26:41,424 --> 00:26:43,560
I've been wrong for half my life.

325
00:26:43,568 --> 00:26:46,312
I'm really sorry, I was wrong.

326
00:26:46,320 --> 00:26:47,470
I was wrong, I'm really sorry.

327
00:26:47,472 --> 00:26:48,744
Aunt Chan, it's okay.

328
00:26:53,176 --> 00:26:56,600
I felt so frustrated that I feel like I am suffocating.

329
00:26:58,600 --> 00:27:00,416
I need to take the medicine first.

330
00:27:00,416 --> 00:27:03,424
Wait for me right here.

331
00:27:03,424 --> 00:27:04,070
Calm down.

332
00:27:04,072 --> 00:27:06,512
Yang, take me take medicine. I can't take it anymore.

333
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:11,408
Wait here for me, I'll be right back. Please.

334
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:12,344
Okay.

335
00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:40,424
Mom, slowly.

336
00:27:41,672 --> 00:27:42,952
Slowly.

337
00:27:50,016 --> 00:27:51,184
Mother.

338
00:27:51,192 --> 00:27:52,816
Just sit down and wait here.

339
00:27:52,810 --> 00:27:55,464
I'll go to the doctor or Aunt Jia to let them check your condition.

340
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:56,960
No need to.

341
00:27:59,264 --> 00:28:00,600
Are you better now?

342
00:28:03,048 --> 00:28:05,072
Not quite yet.

343
00:28:05,330 --> 00:28:07,500
But I'll probably get better after I sit here for a while.

344
00:28:07,512 --> 00:28:09,664
You don't have to call someone here.

345
00:28:11,168 --> 00:28:13,048
Just find something to fan me.

346
00:28:37,568 --> 00:28:39,184
- Ngek.
- Yes?

347
00:28:39,192 --> 00:28:40,776
Did you see Tian?

348
00:28:40,800 --> 00:28:43,464
I saw him in the garden.

349
00:28:45,456 --> 00:28:48,600
It's late at night already. What is he doing in the garden?

350
00:29:32,224 --> 00:29:33,240
Mom.

351
00:29:33,464 --> 00:29:37,320
If you get better now, I'll see Tian.

352
00:29:37,328 --> 00:29:38,600
It's windy outside.

353
00:29:38,608 --> 00:29:39,856
No!

354
00:29:42,288 --> 00:29:43,704
Why?

355
00:29:47,296 --> 00:29:49,144
Are you pretending to be sick?

356
00:29:50,600 --> 00:29:52,576
What are you going to do?

357
00:30:46,600 --> 00:30:47,600
Who are you?

358
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:10,824
Tian.

359
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:13,960
Tian.

360
00:31:16,184 --> 00:31:17,432
Tian.

361
00:31:19,904 --> 00:31:20,760
Mother...

362
00:31:37,048 --> 00:31:38,432
Tian.

363
00:31:57,304 --> 00:31:58,416
Tian.

364
00:32:06,856 --> 00:32:07,816
Tian.

365
00:32:08,288 --> 00:32:09,384
Tian.

366
00:32:10,224 --> 00:32:12,184
Blood. What happened to you?

367
00:32:12,184 --> 00:32:14,600
What's wrong? What's going on?

368
00:32:14,624 --> 00:32:16,000
Someone attacked me.

369
00:32:42,456 --> 00:32:44,160
I almost killed you, Tian.

370
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:54,032
Just a little bit.

371
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,664
It's done.

372
00:32:58,704 --> 00:33:00,600
Are you in a lot of pain?

373
00:33:00,632 --> 00:33:03,208
It's okay, Bua. Thank you very much.

374
00:33:03,224 --> 00:33:04,352
Yes.

375
00:33:09,272 --> 00:33:12,544
I let the workers go after him, but there was no sign of anything.

376
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:16,248
I will set up a guard team tonight

377
00:33:16,264 --> 00:33:17,744
in case the villain comes back.

378
00:33:17,872 --> 00:33:18,664
Tian.

379
00:33:19,288 --> 00:33:21,672
Do you know who it is?

380
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:24,712
No, Father.

381
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:27,600
It was very dark in that area.

382
00:33:28,248 --> 00:33:30,160
So why don't you sleep since it's late night?

383
00:33:30,168 --> 00:33:31,936
Why did you go to the garden?

384
00:33:36,352 --> 00:33:38,176
I went for a walk.

385
00:33:39,592 --> 00:33:42,600
The person who attacked me must be a bandit around here.

386
00:33:42,624 --> 00:33:47,120
He probably planned to rob an outsider like us for money.

387
00:33:48,720 --> 00:33:49,712
Really?

388
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:55,064
Yes, Father.

389
00:34:19,512 --> 00:34:20,600
Bao.

390
00:34:21,312 --> 00:34:23,600
When you went out to find the villain,

391
00:34:25,128 --> 00:34:26,600
was there anything wrong?

392
00:34:27,384 --> 00:34:28,864
Not at all, Sir.

393
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:31,344
There was no trace inside the shrine.

394
00:34:31,624 --> 00:34:33,112
Everything is fine.

395
00:34:33,568 --> 00:34:34,950
But Mr. Tian said that when the thief arrived,

396
00:34:34,968 --> 00:34:38,600
he just caught the thief first. I don't think it was right.

397
00:34:39,370 --> 00:34:41,784
Because where Mr. Tian was attacked was an open space.

398
00:34:42,128 --> 00:34:45,648
If they didn't plan to face each other, there's probably no easy way to meet.

399
00:34:48,256 --> 00:34:51,600
I also thought that it wasn't a thief.

400
00:34:52,088 --> 00:34:53,952
And that Tian was attacked like this,

401
00:34:56,328 --> 00:34:58,712
it's probably related to his secret.

402
00:35:05,712 --> 00:35:07,176
Why did you do this?

403
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:09,328
Did you call the thief to come here?

404
00:35:09,336 --> 00:35:10,504
It's not me.

405
00:35:10,504 --> 00:35:13,600
Are you saying that everything that happened was a coincidence?

406
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,940
You said you were remorseful and wanted to be ordained.

407
00:35:15,952 --> 00:35:18,040
You let me call Tian for you. I did it.

408
00:35:18,488 --> 00:35:20,392
What has gotten into you?

409
00:35:20,408 --> 00:35:22,520
Why do you only think of hurting Tian?

410
00:35:24,520 --> 00:35:26,048
And did you see it just now?

411
00:35:26,600 --> 00:35:28,920
He didn't mention anything about us.

412
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:31,600
If he said we were the ones who took him out,

413
00:35:31,624 --> 00:35:34,320
we might be kicked out of the family right away.

414
00:35:34,352 --> 00:35:35,984
But he didn't.

415
00:35:38,296 --> 00:35:40,120
Have you seen his goodness?

416
00:35:40,792 --> 00:35:42,544
What does it have to do with me?

417
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:45,112
No matter how good he is,

418
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:47,552
he's the one who are going to take everything from you.

419
00:35:47,560 --> 00:35:49,360
So what should I do?

420
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:52,800
I'm trying to figure out and expose his secret,

421
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:54,272
but it was unsuccessful.

422
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:57,976
If you don't want me to hurt him again,

423
00:35:57,984 --> 00:36:01,376
tell me what's the secret.

424
00:36:11,376 --> 00:36:12,600
Tian.

425
00:36:13,552 --> 00:36:15,256
How come you were there?

426
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:19,144
Were Chan and Yang involved in this?

427
00:36:19,784 --> 00:36:22,872
I told you already that I went for a walk.

428
00:36:24,016 --> 00:36:28,120
Hey, don't think I can't see that you are hiding something.

429
00:36:28,504 --> 00:36:32,072
If this Chan was involved, I won't be surprised.

430
00:36:32,392 --> 00:36:36,008
But if it was Yang as well, you have to tell me.

431
00:36:36,416 --> 00:36:38,336
Don't worry, Mother.

432
00:36:38,808 --> 00:36:41,000
Yang will never hurt me.

433
00:36:41,872 --> 00:36:44,144
Don't be too confident about it.

434
00:36:44,368 --> 00:36:47,744
Even the brothers from the same mother, they could kill each other.

435
00:36:48,312 --> 00:36:49,792
No matter how much they love each other,

436
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:51,640
if there are interests,

437
00:36:51,656 --> 00:36:54,336
they're always ready to hate each other.

438
00:37:03,232 --> 00:37:05,088
What is his secret?

439
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:07,728
Tell me!

440
00:37:12,152 --> 00:37:13,160
I won't.

441
00:37:15,336 --> 00:37:17,304
Even if I die, I won't tell you.

442
00:37:17,304 --> 00:37:18,600
Yang!

443
00:38:04,344 --> 00:38:06,264
Oh, Tian.

444
00:38:07,296 --> 00:38:10,720
Aren't you going to bed yet? What are you doing here?

445
00:38:10,752 --> 00:38:14,616
If the thief comes back, what will you do?

446
00:38:14,848 --> 00:38:17,248
He probably won't come back.

447
00:38:17,856 --> 00:38:20,320
The lights are on.

448
00:38:21,248 --> 00:38:22,480
Right.

449
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:29,616
So what are you thinking?

450
00:38:31,784 --> 00:38:34,336
What exactly happened?

451
00:38:34,376 --> 00:38:36,216
When I fixed your wound,

452
00:38:36,240 --> 00:38:39,688
I saw that both you and Yang acted strange.

453
00:38:47,304 --> 00:38:48,400
Bua.

454
00:38:48,416 --> 00:38:49,632
Yes?

455
00:38:52,216 --> 00:38:54,864
Actually, I didn't go for a walk.

456
00:38:55,984 --> 00:38:57,800
Yang was the one who took me there.

457
00:38:58,072 --> 00:39:03,832
Mother can see that the people who did this were Aunt Chan and Yang...

458
00:39:04,264 --> 00:39:06,968
I don't know if it was a coincidence

459
00:39:08,200 --> 00:39:11,184
or if Aunt Chan intentionally let it be like this.

460
00:39:12,304 --> 00:39:13,440
So...

461
00:39:14,168 --> 00:39:19,616
Tian... Did you have doubts about Yang?

462
00:39:19,616 --> 00:39:21,304
Not at all.

463
00:39:22,528 --> 00:39:25,008
I believe that no matter what happens,

464
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:27,408
Yang will never hurt me.

465
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:31,616
I never doubt anything about him.

466
00:39:33,536 --> 00:39:34,856
Yes.

467
00:39:44,816 --> 00:39:47,872
What? Did Tian get away?

468
00:39:47,872 --> 00:39:49,784
And did he see your face?

469
00:39:50,256 --> 00:39:51,056
No.

470
00:39:53,304 --> 00:39:54,568
How could you miss it?

471
00:39:55,184 --> 00:39:57,184
You usually never miss.

472
00:40:00,648 --> 00:40:02,256
But what's going on between you and him?

473
00:40:02,264 --> 00:40:04,248
Why did you want me to kill him?

474
00:40:04,248 --> 00:40:05,784
He seems to be a nice guy.

475
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:08,296
Do you know him?

476
00:40:12,336 --> 00:40:13,320
No.

477
00:40:13,832 --> 00:40:16,144
According to his face, he seems harmless.

478
00:40:16,448 --> 00:40:19,760
He's harmless to you, but not me.

479
00:40:19,776 --> 00:40:22,696
He interfered in my business and gave me a hard time.

480
00:40:27,808 --> 00:40:31,600
It's ok. You go back and rest now.

481
00:40:31,616 --> 00:40:33,672
I'll contact you later.

482
00:40:35,712 --> 00:40:37,200
I won't do this job anymore.

483
00:40:38,712 --> 00:40:40,056
Why?

484
00:40:41,296 --> 00:40:42,992
It's too dangerous.

485
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:46,256
The man you want me to kill has money and power.

486
00:40:46,272 --> 00:40:47,448
I don't want to risk my life.

487
00:40:48,256 --> 00:40:49,552
You have to do it.

488
00:40:49,688 --> 00:40:51,208
Did you forget

489
00:40:51,216 --> 00:40:53,808
that your sister's condition has improved

490
00:40:53,832 --> 00:40:55,896
because of the medicine I gave you.

491
00:40:57,432 --> 00:40:58,752
You choose.

492
00:40:59,864 --> 00:41:04,504
If he's not dead, your sister will.

493
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:35,000
Zhang Zhitian

494
00:41:48,416 --> 00:41:51,192
I looked around the shrine and couldn't find you.

495
00:41:51,624 --> 00:41:55,216
I thought that you would come to see Mr. Zhang here.

496
00:42:01,136 --> 00:42:02,544
I miss Zhang.

497
00:42:06,880 --> 00:42:08,576
Since he passed away,

498
00:42:10,376 --> 00:42:13,080
The Five Dragons Association was never the same.

499
00:42:16,792 --> 00:42:18,776
If Mr. Zhang was still alive,

500
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:25,344
he would be your consultant and could handle the chaos on behalf of you.

501
00:42:37,088 --> 00:42:39,224
He was the younger brother that I loved.

502
00:42:41,312 --> 00:42:44,552
He was the person who understood my feelings the most.

503
00:42:48,736 --> 00:42:50,264
Zhang is good,

504
00:42:51,736 --> 00:42:52,848
hard-working,

505
00:42:53,720 --> 00:42:55,000
and considerate.

506
00:42:59,120 --> 00:43:04,080
Whatever work I let him do, he always did well.

507
00:43:04,328 --> 00:43:06,000
Never failed at all.

508
00:43:10,584 --> 00:43:12,792
But he shouldn't be a homosexual.

509
00:43:18,200 --> 00:43:20,136
All the goodness

510
00:43:20,592 --> 00:43:22,544
that Zhang did

511
00:43:23,496 --> 00:43:28,384
couldn't make you overlook this?

512
00:43:29,560 --> 00:43:31,472
If he could choose,

513
00:43:32,200 --> 00:43:35,424
he himself would want you to understand

514
00:43:35,424 --> 00:43:39,456
and accept what he was.

515
00:43:45,848 --> 00:43:47,600
It already happened.

516
00:43:48,784 --> 00:43:50,480
I couldn't fix anything.

517
00:43:52,624 --> 00:43:54,408
And if you could turn back time?

518
00:43:56,696 --> 00:43:58,840
If you could go back,

519
00:44:00,200 --> 00:44:02,080
would you still

520
00:44:03,208 --> 00:44:06,480
drive him out of the Five Dragons Associations?

521
00:44:16,480 --> 00:44:18,544
I will have to make the same decision.

522
00:44:20,496 --> 00:44:24,616
No one accepts a homosexual

523
00:44:26,352 --> 00:44:29,272
to manage and control people.

524
00:44:54,368 --> 00:44:56,296
I've made up my mind.

525
00:44:56,600 --> 00:44:58,070
I will stay here further.

526
00:44:58,080 --> 00:45:01,768
Is it alright? Will Mr. Song have any doubts?

527
00:45:02,136 --> 00:45:05,000
I will tell Father that I would like to play around a little more.

528
00:45:05,024 --> 00:45:07,096
He probably wouldn't mind.

529
00:45:07,800 --> 00:45:10,624
Since we've been here, I don't want to come here in vain.

530
00:45:10,632 --> 00:45:13,688
Because if we go back, we will never know

531
00:45:13,704 --> 00:45:16,096
where we can find out about this mushroom.

532
00:45:16,696 --> 00:45:20,400
Yes, let's do this.

533
00:45:22,288 --> 00:45:23,752
That is...

534
00:45:23,752 --> 00:45:25,184
What is it?

535
00:45:28,456 --> 00:45:29,696
Mr. Song.

536
00:45:30,072 --> 00:45:33,320
I thought we'd never meet again, Doctor Qi.

537
00:45:33,808 --> 00:45:35,200
Doctor Qi.

538
00:45:40,288 --> 00:45:42,744
The people at the market have talked

539
00:45:42,760 --> 00:45:46,608
that people from the Song Family came to this shrine.

540
00:45:46,624 --> 00:45:52,304
So I thought that you come here to pay homage to the gods every year.

541
00:45:52,904 --> 00:45:55,904
But I was so busy that I couldn't rush here.

542
00:45:55,912 --> 00:45:58,424
I need to treat the sick urgently.

543
00:45:58,696 --> 00:46:01,944
I thought that we would miss each other again.

544
00:46:02,512 --> 00:46:06,848
Mr. Song, Madam Li, how are you?

545
00:46:06,856 --> 00:46:10,208
I am sick once in a while, like an old man.

546
00:46:10,240 --> 00:46:14,056
But Jia has provided me treatment.

547
00:46:15,000 --> 00:46:17,000
I'm fine.

548
00:46:17,016 --> 00:46:21,248
I let Bao call Jia for you. She would be happy to meet you.

549
00:46:24,264 --> 00:46:25,968
How about you, Madam Chan?

550
00:46:26,160 --> 00:46:27,624
Good too.

551
00:46:29,000 --> 00:46:30,464
Bua?

552
00:46:31,184 --> 00:46:32,280
Yes.

553
00:46:34,416 --> 00:46:39,784
These two must be Mr. Tian and Mr. Yang.

554
00:46:39,800 --> 00:46:46,320
But I can't remember which one is Tian or Yang since I saw you when you were little.

555
00:46:46,808 --> 00:46:48,896
The one on the right is Tian.

556
00:46:48,920 --> 00:46:51,096
The one on the left is Yang.

557
00:46:53,392 --> 00:46:59,000
These two have grown up and look handsome like you when you were young, Sir.

558
00:47:03,264 --> 00:47:07,480
Everything is packed. Are you going back now?

559
00:47:08,520 --> 00:47:12,448
It's really a pity that I'm a bit late.

560
00:47:12,744 --> 00:47:14,320
Not late at all, Doctor.

561
00:47:14,840 --> 00:47:16,360
We still have time.

562
00:47:21,640 --> 00:47:23,496
Let's have some tea.

563
00:47:32,304 --> 00:47:36,192
Thank you so much Doctor Qi for taking such good care of us.

564
00:47:36,616 --> 00:47:40,888
Mr. Song, Madam Li, Madam Chan, take care of your health.

565
00:47:40,888 --> 00:47:42,448
Have a safe trip back.

566
00:47:45,000 --> 00:47:45,950
Mr. Yang.

567
00:47:45,960 --> 00:47:47,192
Let's go.

568
00:47:51,440 --> 00:47:52,592
Doctor Qi.

569
00:47:52,592 --> 00:47:54,768
Oh, Bua.

570
00:47:56,344 --> 00:47:58,584
I would like to discuss with you.

571
00:48:12,944 --> 00:48:14,048
This is...

572
00:48:14,056 --> 00:48:16,992
Do you know this mushroom?

573
00:48:18,488 --> 00:48:20,520
What mushroom is it, Doctor?

574
00:48:20,536 --> 00:48:23,096
Why do you look so shocked?

575
00:48:24,096 --> 00:48:27,208
This mushroom is called

576
00:48:27,696 --> 00:48:29,000
blood sucking mushroom.

577
00:48:29,016 --> 00:48:31,000
Blood sucking mushroom?

578
00:48:31,560 --> 00:48:35,088
Why is the name so scary?

579
00:48:35,352 --> 00:48:37,224
And it's very rare, isn't it?

580
00:48:37,368 --> 00:48:42,240
Bua and I went to the drugstores and no one knows it.

581
00:48:42,808 --> 00:48:46,768
It does not appear naturally.

582
00:48:47,136 --> 00:48:50,536
This mushroom is secret knowledge.

583
00:48:50,856 --> 00:48:52,736
Secret knowledge?

584
00:48:53,832 --> 00:48:58,328
This is taking mushrooms that grow on insects

585
00:48:58,328 --> 00:49:01,000
or we called them orchids,

586
00:49:01,080 --> 00:49:04,368
put together with some special ingredients.

587
00:49:05,440 --> 00:49:10,512
Just put the thing you want it to grow on in.

588
00:49:12,192 --> 00:49:14,064
As far as I see,

589
00:49:14,720 --> 00:49:20,496
this mushroom grew from the remains of living things.

590
00:49:23,064 --> 00:49:24,744
Remains of living things?

591
00:49:26,096 --> 00:49:31,856
Could you check what remains this mushroom grew on?

592
00:49:33,216 --> 00:49:36,704
Only those who made it will know.

593
00:49:38,376 --> 00:49:42,432
Where did you two get this mushroom from?

594
00:49:46,136 --> 00:49:48,496
At the backyard of Song's house.

595
00:50:04,520 --> 00:50:06,336
You are here.

596
00:50:08,528 --> 00:50:09,816
Jia.

597
00:50:11,144 --> 00:50:15,456
So glad to see you. How are you?

598
00:50:15,496 --> 00:50:19,232
Do you have any difficulty living here?

599
00:50:19,944 --> 00:50:21,208
Not at all.

600
00:50:21,488 --> 00:50:27,744
You know that an old man like me was not someone who wanted any comfort.

601
00:50:28,032 --> 00:50:31,832
Otherwise I wouldn't have come out of the family.

602
00:50:33,464 --> 00:50:36,448
I know, I remember it.

603
00:50:36,456 --> 00:50:41,960
You told me that you would use your knowledge of medicine and herbs to help a lot of people.

604
00:50:43,416 --> 00:50:48,944
Thinking about that time, if you didn't save me,

605
00:50:49,800 --> 00:50:51,752
I was probably dead.

606
00:50:52,512 --> 00:50:57,624
You didn't just save my life, but also gave me a new life.

607
00:50:58,208 --> 00:51:04,832
You taught me until I have knowledge of medicines to save people.

608
00:51:06,224 --> 00:51:08,912
And what I taught you,

609
00:51:09,272 --> 00:51:12,056
Are you using it in the right way?

610
00:51:15,000 --> 00:51:16,592
Is it correct?

611
00:51:18,584 --> 00:51:19,728
Yes.

612
00:51:21,320 --> 00:51:22,608
If so,

613
00:51:23,864 --> 00:51:25,048
this mushroom...

614
00:51:27,688 --> 00:51:30,768
How did this mushroom appear in the back of the Song's house?

615
00:51:31,552 --> 00:51:33,000
What are you doing?

616
00:51:34,768 --> 00:51:36,528
I didn't do anything.

617
00:51:37,376 --> 00:51:43,608
These mushrooms probably grew from the ants that took the orchids that I kept and eat at its nest.

618
00:51:43,616 --> 00:51:45,288
So the mushrooms grew out there.

619
00:51:48,144 --> 00:51:49,320
Really?

620
00:51:51,232 --> 00:51:53,496
And who shows you this mushroom?

621
00:51:54,864 --> 00:51:58,288
If this mushroom actually grew in the ant nest like you said,

622
00:51:58,296 --> 00:52:02,000
you don't have to worry about who gave it to me.

623
00:52:10,392 --> 00:52:13,728
Strange thing? There is strange thing.

624
00:52:13,752 --> 00:52:16,056
What's the matter, Sir?

625
00:52:16,500 --> 00:52:18,736
Dong, a worker at my house has died.

626
00:52:19,528 --> 00:52:21,360
His body disappeared.

627
00:52:22,120 --> 00:52:25,704
The whole family suspected that it was Li who did it.

628
00:52:26,032 --> 00:52:29,824
So what do you think?

629
00:52:31,232 --> 00:52:32,704
I suspect

630
00:52:34,656 --> 00:52:36,184
that it was Li too.

631
00:52:37,000 --> 00:52:41,000
But I am surprised. Why did she do it?

632
00:52:42,000 --> 00:52:43,552
What reason she has?

633
00:52:46,728 --> 00:52:51,208
There were mushrooms like this producing at your house, right?

634
00:52:51,552 --> 00:52:53,000
Yes, Doctor.

635
00:52:53,016 --> 00:52:55,264
How do you have this mushroom?

636
00:52:55,280 --> 00:52:58,224
Try digging the area where this mushroom grew

637
00:52:58,224 --> 00:53:00,096
and see if there is anything there.

638
00:53:00,104 --> 00:53:02,320
Tell me immediately if you find something.

639
00:53:02,344 --> 00:53:07,784
If I have finished my errands here, I will meet you in Phra Nakhon.

640
00:53:09,784 --> 00:53:12,520
Someone has been investigating the mushrooms from Dong's body?

641
00:53:13,104 --> 00:53:15,144
How did you answer Doctor Qi?

642
00:53:15,160 --> 00:53:19,168
I made up an excuse, but I didn't think he would believe it.

643
00:53:19,192 --> 00:53:21,080
What shall we do?

644
00:53:21,520 --> 00:53:23,648
Who is investigating this?

645
00:53:27,440 --> 00:53:29,000
So how do we know?

646
00:53:58,640 --> 00:54:00,784
So tired.

647
00:54:00,784 --> 00:54:04,000
Hey, you were so happy when you went there, weren't you. Hurry.

648
00:54:43,936 --> 00:54:48,136
It's good to go to Chonburi this time. We have met Doctor Qi.

649
00:54:48,400 --> 00:54:50,216
He is still the same.

650
00:54:51,704 --> 00:54:53,000
And...

651
00:54:53,848 --> 00:54:57,192
What did you talk to him for a long time?

652
00:55:09,552 --> 00:55:11,312
What's wrong?

653
00:55:11,840 --> 00:55:13,808
Why are you looking at me like that?

654
00:55:19,792 --> 00:55:21,064
Nothing.

655
00:55:23,280 --> 00:55:27,512
We talked like the old men

656
00:55:29,480 --> 00:55:31,776
with deteriorating health.

657
00:55:33,800 --> 00:55:37,176
You aren't old yet. You're still young.

658
00:55:42,000 --> 00:55:44,536
Among all my three wives,

659
00:55:49,456 --> 00:55:52,000
Bua is the most lovable wife

660
00:55:54,680 --> 00:55:58,080
because she is humble and never asked for anything.

661
00:56:00,000 --> 00:56:01,832
Chan is the most worried

662
00:56:02,952 --> 00:56:04,808
because she likes to cause trouble

663
00:56:05,592 --> 00:56:07,168
and won't surrender to anyone.

664
00:56:08,480 --> 00:56:09,840
As for you,

665
00:56:11,184 --> 00:56:13,776
you are the most respectful wife

666
00:56:16,864 --> 00:56:18,384
because you are good

667
00:56:20,232 --> 00:56:21,584
and talented.

668
00:56:23,704 --> 00:56:25,480
You can help me do my job.

669
00:56:27,344 --> 00:56:29,184
You know my heart.

670
00:56:31,776 --> 00:56:36,584
You are also the madam of the Song family.

671
00:56:40,000 --> 00:56:42,208
Thank you, Sir.

672
00:56:44,000 --> 00:56:46,000
Even Homer sometimes nods.

673
00:56:47,768 --> 00:56:49,656
The wise man can make a mistake sometimes.

674
00:56:52,152 --> 00:56:53,704
No matter how good you are,

675
00:56:54,672 --> 00:56:56,408
there is still a mistake.

676
00:57:09,192 --> 00:57:11,224
Do you have anything to tell me?

677
00:57:21,872 --> 00:57:24,272
There's nothing, Sir.

678
00:57:25,512 --> 00:57:26,768
Mr. Song.

679
00:57:27,248 --> 00:57:31,512
Are you alright? Why are you asking me this?

680
00:57:32,824 --> 00:57:34,224
Sir.

681
00:57:35,496 --> 00:57:37,496
If you have something,

682
00:57:37,944 --> 00:57:41,152
you can ask me directly.

683
00:57:42,896 --> 00:57:45,312
You talk like this,

684
00:57:45,680 --> 00:57:47,496
I'm not feeling well at all.

685
00:57:51,736 --> 00:57:53,352
That's fine if you don't have anything to tell me.

686
00:57:57,000 --> 00:58:00,080
Please know that I understand you.

687
00:58:03,000 --> 00:58:04,904
I don't want you to be stressed.

688
00:58:39,600 --> 00:58:42,408
Recently, Mr. Song talks strangely.

689
00:58:42,616 --> 00:58:44,448
Did he say anything to you?

690
00:58:44,840 --> 00:58:46,520
No, Madam.

691
00:58:47,752 --> 00:58:49,352
What's wrong?

692
00:58:50,488 --> 00:58:52,416
I got a bad feeling.

693
00:58:53,112 --> 00:58:55,240
About Dong's body at the back of the house.

694
00:59:04,200 --> 00:59:06,168
You can be at ease.

695
00:59:06,432 --> 00:59:08,800
My fermented water is fatal.

696
00:59:08,816 --> 00:59:11,776
It can eat into human bones

697
00:59:11,792 --> 00:59:13,520
without traces left.

698
00:59:20,000 --> 00:59:22,112
Nothing is buried here, Sir.

699
00:59:26,000 --> 00:59:29,336
These days, I can't sleep tight at all.

700
00:59:30,488 --> 00:59:33,408
The only way to end everything is

701
00:59:33,928 --> 00:59:36,472
to hurry and let Tian take the position.

702
00:59:49,880 --> 00:59:51,360
Are you sure

703
00:59:52,272 --> 00:59:56,480
that the workers picked mushrooms from here?

704
00:59:57,072 --> 00:59:58,720
It must be here, Sir.

705
01:00:01,752 --> 01:00:03,472
Then there must be something.

706
01:00:30,168 --> 01:00:31,448
A human tooth.

707
01:00:33,768 --> 01:00:36,120
Whose teeth would drop here?

708
01:00:38,192 --> 01:00:39,112
Or...

709
01:00:39,736 --> 01:00:42,632
Is there a corpse buried here, Sir?

710
01:00:44,200 --> 01:00:45,528
If there is really a corpse here,

711
01:00:46,528 --> 01:00:50,448
then why is there only one tooth left?

712
01:01:03,744 --> 01:01:06,272
How did your man work?

713
01:01:06,280 --> 01:01:09,568
Instead of killing Tian, I almost got into trouble as well.

714
01:01:09,960 --> 01:01:12,568
If you did everything according to the plan,

715
01:01:12,768 --> 01:01:15,536
my subordinate would have more time to handle this.

716
01:01:15,952 --> 01:01:18,592
What Mr. Ma said was correct, Madam.

717
01:01:18,600 --> 01:01:20,592
- Nuan!
- Yes, Madam.

718
01:01:20,840 --> 01:01:24,592
How much time will it take just stabbing with a knife?

719
01:01:25,152 --> 01:01:27,488
I think instead of fighting,

720
01:01:27,480 --> 01:01:31,328
we should figure out a way to get rid of Tian. Isn't it better?

721
01:01:35,288 --> 01:01:36,896
It must be difficult.

722
01:01:37,696 --> 01:01:41,232
He was almost assassinated like this. He would probably be more careful.

723
01:01:45,408 --> 01:01:48,768
Previously, you said that

724
01:01:48,952 --> 01:01:51,168
Tian has a serious secret.

725
01:01:51,168 --> 01:01:54,224
Even Li had to kill a guy to cover up.

726
01:01:55,500 --> 01:01:58,000
What if we uncover this secret?

727
01:02:00,616 --> 01:02:04,000
I've been trying to search for that secret for a long time,

728
01:02:04,020 --> 01:02:05,640
but it is still unsuccessful.

729
01:02:05,856 --> 01:02:07,000
Right.

730
01:02:07,472 --> 01:02:09,792
The more they cover up,

731
01:02:09,800 --> 01:02:12,048
The more it is important.

732
01:02:12,752 --> 01:02:17,136
What is the secret of the Song Family's number one heir?

733
01:02:17,608 --> 01:02:19,568
I would like to know that.

734
01:02:22,536 --> 01:02:26,480
So while you are planning to assassinate Tian,

735
01:02:27,000 --> 01:02:29,776
I will find out this secret.

736
01:02:30,344 --> 01:02:31,704
What do you think?

737
01:02:32,856 --> 01:02:34,000
Good.

738
01:02:41,232 --> 01:02:42,360
Jiu.

739
01:02:43,736 --> 01:02:45,664
Fu, Mei.

740
01:02:47,456 --> 01:02:48,304
Is anyone there?

741
01:02:48,304 --> 01:02:50,048
I'm hurt.

742
01:02:50,200 --> 01:02:51,000
Mei.

743
01:02:52,000 --> 01:02:53,000
Mei.

744
01:02:53,240 --> 01:02:54,872
I'm hurt.

745
01:02:56,200 --> 01:02:57,488
Move.

746
01:02:58,000 --> 01:02:59,000
Mei.

747
01:03:00,576 --> 01:03:02,000
Eat this.

748
01:03:13,304 --> 01:03:16,000
Jiu, there's no Mei's medicine left.

749
01:03:24,328 --> 01:03:28,104
I think Mei's condition is serious. You should take her to the doctor.

750
01:03:28,424 --> 01:03:29,616
I have taken her there.

751
01:03:30,624 --> 01:03:33,456
The doctor said that there was no medicine to cure her.

752
01:03:33,800 --> 01:03:35,688
Besides, it's a war time.

753
01:03:35,888 --> 01:03:37,480
There is no western medicine as well.

754
01:03:39,128 --> 01:03:42,120
Now I'm just relying on Chinese medicine from someone I know.

755
01:03:44,104 --> 01:03:46,088
How long have you been treating her?

756
01:03:46,104 --> 01:03:47,440
Isn't she better?

757
01:03:49,072 --> 01:03:51,560
Her condition improved only after taking the pills.

758
01:03:52,000 --> 01:03:54,464
But when the medicine wears off, the symptoms relapsed.

759
01:04:11,488 --> 01:04:13,304
So what do you do next?

760
01:04:14,616 --> 01:04:16,768
Are you going to let Mei be like this?

761
01:04:20,448 --> 01:04:21,960
I won't do this job anymore.

762
01:04:22,192 --> 01:04:23,352
You have to do it.

763
01:04:23,616 --> 01:04:25,192
Did you forget

764
01:04:25,192 --> 01:04:27,760
that your sister's condition has improved

765
01:04:27,768 --> 01:04:29,792
because of the medicine I gave you.

766
01:04:30,160 --> 01:04:31,560
You choose.

767
01:04:32,000 --> 01:04:36,768
If he's not dead, your sister will.

768
01:04:50,896 --> 01:04:52,448
I think you should go back today.

769
01:04:53,096 --> 01:04:54,128
I'll send you off.

770
01:05:10,000 --> 01:05:11,136
Let's go.

771
01:05:18,328 --> 01:05:21,096
Why did you bring me here today?

772
01:05:21,960 --> 01:05:23,144
It's a shortcut.

773
01:05:24,672 --> 01:05:27,000
I've never used this way before.

774
01:05:27,360 --> 01:05:30,680
Even though it's a bit deserted, it's pleasant.

775
01:05:33,088 --> 01:05:34,632
There are a lot of trees.

776
01:05:34,648 --> 01:05:36,024
Do you think so?

777
01:06:34,736 --> 01:06:35,920
Jiu.

778
01:06:36,344 --> 01:06:37,960
Is there anything wrong?

779
01:06:40,320 --> 01:06:41,272
Nothing.

780
01:06:46,288 --> 01:06:47,600
Tian, dodge!

781
01:06:52,672 --> 01:06:54,848
Go along this way. You'll reach your home.

782
01:06:54,856 --> 01:06:56,224
Hurry, go!

783
01:06:56,928 --> 01:06:58,144
Go, Tian. Quickly!

784
01:07:06,800 --> 01:07:07,608
Gui.

785
01:07:07,608 --> 01:07:09,248
Yeah, it's me.

786
01:07:09,400 --> 01:07:12,000
You are evil. Dare to lie to Mr. Ma.

787
01:07:12,016 --> 01:07:13,640
How can you do this?

788
01:07:25,000 --> 01:07:25,968
Mr. Ma.

789
01:07:31,120 --> 01:07:32,880
What's up?

790
01:07:35,392 --> 01:07:39,168
I came to look for you. You have been missing for a long time.

791
01:07:41,480 --> 01:07:42,600
Sir.

792
01:07:42,616 --> 01:07:44,368
He knows Tian.

793
01:07:45,720 --> 01:07:49,744
Just now, I went to shoot Tian, but Jiu saved him, so I missed it.

794
01:07:49,744 --> 01:07:51,960
Otherwise, Tian would already be dead by now.

795
01:07:52,000 --> 01:07:53,200
Jerk.

796
01:07:53,928 --> 01:07:57,456
Hey Gui, calm down.

797
01:07:57,456 --> 01:07:59,136
Don't be impulsive.

798
01:07:59,376 --> 01:08:01,952
If Tian dies in our territory,

799
01:08:01,976 --> 01:08:04,680
Big Brother must suspect us.

800
01:08:09,480 --> 01:08:11,728
You can let me kill anyone,

801
01:08:13,440 --> 01:08:15,000
but not this one, I beg you.

802
01:08:15,488 --> 01:08:20,000
So this means you are really close to Tian?

803
01:08:21,224 --> 01:08:23,000
He once helped my siblings.

804
01:08:23,896 --> 01:08:26,848
He is like a benefactor for my siblings just like you.

805
01:08:26,856 --> 01:08:30,568
Bastard, how dare you compare him to Mr. Ma?

806
01:08:30,936 --> 01:08:32,944
Do you want your sister to die?

807
01:08:35,936 --> 01:08:37,864
I understand you.

808
01:08:38,776 --> 01:08:42,832
A person must know gratitude.

809
01:08:43,216 --> 01:08:45,752
I don't want you to be ungrateful.

810
01:08:46,152 --> 01:08:50,568
So I have choices for you.

811
01:09:30,728 --> 01:09:32,864
If those two kids are still with us,

812
01:09:32,864 --> 01:09:35,776
Jiu will do anything for us.

813
01:09:35,784 --> 01:09:39,216
Mr. Tian, someone wants to apply for a job.

814
01:09:40,120 --> 01:09:41,912
I found this tooth.

815
01:09:43,064 --> 01:09:46,520
We have to find out who knows about this mushroom.

816
01:09:47,128 --> 01:09:48,360
Mr. Yang.

